 y388 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">on the shelf, then go out into the field by the houses to do some-</div><div class="t m598 x3e h4 y469 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">thing with the earth; not as we have to do with the earth here; </div><div class="t m700 x3e h4 y12e4 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">no, no. A glorious light shone all about their heads, and they </div><div class="t m9ba x16 h4 y3bc ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">were continually shouting and offering praises to </div><div class="t m720 x9d h30 ya03 ff6 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">God.&quot;—Early </div><div class="t m23d x16 h30 y8d7 ff6 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Writings, page 14. </div><div class="t ma2 x64 h4 ya46 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">4. </div><div class="t m363 x63 h4 y891 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">The earth itself, the very field which Satan claims as his, </div><div class="t m1465 x3e h4 y7f6 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">is to be not only ransomed, but exalted. Our little world, under </div><div class="t m29b x3e h4 y822 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">the curse of sin, the one dark blot in His glorious creation, will </div><div class="t mc6d x3e h4 ya48 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">be honored above all other worlds in the universe of God. Here, </div><div class="t m181 x3e h4 y904 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">where the Son of God tabernacled in humanity, where the King </div><div class="t m11b x3e h4 y159f ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">of glory lived and suffered and died,—here, when He shall make </div><div class="t m1586 x3e h4 y498 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">all things new, the tabernacle of God shall be with men, &apos;and </div><div class="t mb47 x3e h4 y3d8 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">He shall dwell with them, and they shall&apos; be His people, and God </div><div class="t m9ce x3e h4 y4e9 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Himself shall be with them, and be,their God.&apos; </div><div class="t me28 x9 h30 y3a7 ff6 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">&quot;—Desire of Ages, </div><div class="t m165c x16 h30 yf71 ff6 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Page 26. </div><div class="t m52e 